In-air point-of-sale

The Mobile Point-of-Sale solution from Microsoft and its partners, Accenture and Avanade, is based on Microsoft Dynamics AX 2012 for Retail, and is helping transform onboard sales into an online, fast, connected experience.
Deliver experiences

Modern authenticators ensure that only the field worker can log into the machine, preventing lost or stolen devices from being accessed. Biometrics, Virtual SmartCards with TPM chips, and picture passwords are all available for ensuring that only the authorised user can log into their data and apps.
Deliver personalised, interactive experiences with mobile technologies
